[SN]TITLE[SN]
Sports Personality of the Year: How to vote online

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
You can cast your vote for BBC Sports Personality of the Year 2015 by phone or for free online. Online votes are capped at 1.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
VOTE NOW CLOSED
Phone numbers will be shown on screen during the broadcast, and you can find out more about the voting process in our Frequently Asked Questions page.
In order to vote online for BBC Sports Personality of the Year 2015 you will need to register for a BBC iD. REGISTER HERE
Registering only takes a few seconds, and the same BBC iD can then be used across the BBC's interactive platforms to write comments, personalise your BBC Sport app, play games, write reviews, and even vote on Strictly Come Dancing.
Once you have your BBC iD, and are signed in to your account, you are all set.
Simply go to http://www.bbc.co.uk/spoty and click on the Vote Now page.
The winner of the combined phone and online vote will be announced during the show.
Your BBC iD account can only cast one vote in Sports Personality of the Year 2015.
You can vote using your mobile phone, tablet or your home computer. You cannot vote online more than once by using the same BBC iD account details on different devices.
Click here for the BBC iD help pages.
If you are still having issues after going through the above link for help, then you should contact membership@bbc.co.uk.
